{"tid":974898,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【科學神教】16歲台少年阻母「淨化」　教會殺人","createTime":"2019-01-09T08:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T16:53:34.000Z","uid":160807,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"067d9dc004bfd4eb2c73f40cead4486d5ab3f932","tid":974898,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:38:52.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n澳洲雪梨車士活（Chatswood）一處山達基教會，日前發生一少年持刀刺死一名台灣男子事件。事後警方調查，少年也是台灣人，當時他是為了阻止母親接受「淨化儀式」結果雙方發生爭執，他並拿出預藏的刀抵抗，才意外造成憾事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QOCOCfQHWKVCsnEwEErPdg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/16e760ec500502a9b66d23c32b1c1493\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FQOCOCfQHWKVCsnEwEErPdg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F16e760ec500502a9b66d23c32b1c1493&h=dc306e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲16歲台少年阻母「淨化」，教會殺人。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，事件發生於本月3日，在此之前16歲台灣籍少年曾哀求母親不要參加山達基（Scientology）的「淨化儀式」，不料母親仍一意孤行，讓少年為了阻止母親，兩人在教會爆發衝突。<br />\n<br />\n當時教會內成員見狀趕緊將少年趕離教會，不料男子卻從車上，拿出一把25厘米的長刀，闖入教會隨機刺死24歲台灣男子，另刺傷一名30歲男子的手部，及另外兩名男女，隨後遭警方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，近日該案開庭審訊，少年被控告多項罪名，包括傷害、謀殺等，不過少年沒有到場聽訊只由律師代表，並要求7日開庭審訊時，提供一名中文翻譯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_RzL4cPzHm6P3zKHUTb6uw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/0b10a2c6117ce8bf4d67504818f2cbe1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_RzL4cPzHm6P3zKHUTb6uw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F0b10a2c6117ce8bf4d67504818f2cbe1&h=bf00dc44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪梨車士活山達基教會，被信徒譽為「虛擬的伊甸園」。（圖／翻攝自Google Map）<br />\n<br />\n此外，報導也介紹了，發生事件的「山達基」又名「科學神教」和「科學教」，由美國作家哈伯德（L.Ron Hubbard）於1952年創辦，總部位於美國洛杉磯。教派認為每個人都有人生創傷，需找到創傷根源，並透過「淨化」來排除，來提升生命品質。其信眾不乏名人，包括美國著名影星湯姆克魯斯（Tom Cruise）。<br />\n<br />\n另外，發生事件的澳洲教會地點，更是此教亞太區總部，地點位於灣國家公園（Lane Cove National Park）及藍桉步道（Blue Gum Creek）附近，更被信徒譽為「虛擬的伊甸園」。不過更驚人的是，外傳教會內課程，光是一小時課程就高達800澳元（約新台幣1.7萬元），但信徒仍對此趨之若鶩。（編輯：陳昱哲）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/16%E6%AD%B2%E5%8F%B0%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%98%BB%E6%AF%8D-%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96-%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA-113532282.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F16%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%25AF%258D-%25E6%25B7%25A8%25E5%258C%2596-%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E4%25BA%25BA-113532282.html&d=uIcbjDcYwpccDxCubFT6b0jIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=213bb79c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/16%E6%AD%B2%E5%8F%B0%E5%B0%91%E5%B9%B4%E9%98%BB%E6%AF%8D-%E6%B7%A8%E5%8C%96-%E6%95%99%E6%9C%83%E6%AE%BA%E4%BA%BA-113532282.html</a>"},{"pid":"6dcaeddf473a0dd064c3190477080796ab504fb1","tid":974898,"uid":82007,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"勇武孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2fd638ef9e0a71f1d8aae5d7871f1069cc5271","tid":974898,"uid":15,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:44:30.000Z","msg":"殊樂畢比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 殊樂畢比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a37ae6799c5ab0893ce94b5599bdc64b34037ae","tid":974898,"uid":34186,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真勇武，成功拯救唔知幾多個家庭"},{"pid":"28f7445b2d771de8191b2303a8bf6e3f36cc48ec","tid":974898,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"真‧孝子"},{"pid":"aa63327a18ace5605ab93368ef454c18bd275b03","tid"